---
title: GLOW in Asia XIII 2022 Online Special at The Chinese University of Hong Kong 
date: 2022-08-04
  
---
The [13th Generative Linguistics in the Old World in Asia (GLOW in Asia XIII) 2022 Online Special](https://ling.cuhk.edu.hk/glowxiii/index.php) has been held in Hong Kong, March 6-8 2024, organized by the Department of Linguistics and Modern Languages, The Chinese University of Hong Kong. 
